graphql.query:
mutation ($payload:CciCreateModuleInput!)
{
	cciCreateModule (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		tenantCode
		systemName
		channelHash
		channelParty
		channelComponent
		channelName
		flowHash
		flowParty
		flowReceiverParty
		flowComponent
		flowReceiverComponent
		flowInterfaceName
		flowInterfaceNamespace
		version
		parameterGroup
		name
		parameterName
		parameterValue
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
